 he met nothing for ten minutes but kept running into dead ends twice he took the same wrong turning finally he found a new route and started to jog along it his wandlight waving making his shadow flicker and distort on the hedge walls then he rounded another corner and found himself facing a skrewt 
 
 cedric was right it was enormous ten feet long it looked more like a giant scorpion than anything its long sting was curled over its back its thick armor glinted in the light from wand which he pointed at it 
 
 stupefy 
 
 the spell hit the armor and rebounded harry ducked just in time but could smell burning hair it had singed the top of his head the skrewt issued a blast of fire from its end and flew forward toward him 
 
 impedimenta harry yelled the spell hit the armor again and ricocheted off harry staggered back a few paces and fell over impedimenta 
 
