 high overhead something black and flapping approached then veered paid no attention he just kept walking 
 the jungle thinned a bit beyond the next bog luke saw dwelling its odd little windows shedding a warm yellow light in thedamp he skirted the mire and crouching low entered the cottage 
 yoda stood smiling inside his small green hand clutching his walking stick forsupport waiting for you i was he nodded 
 he motioned luke to sit in a corner the boy was struck by how much morefrail manner tremor to the hand a weakness to the voice it madeluke afraid to speak to betray his shock at the old condition 
