 the creature hobbled over to his bed still chuckling and with great effort laydown soon will i rest yes forever sleep earned it i have 
 luke shook his head you die master let you 
 trained well and strong with the force are not that strong twilightis upon me and soon night must fall that is the way of thingsthe way of theforce 
 but i need your help luke insisted i want to complete my training thegreat teacher leave him was too much still to understand taken so much from yoda already and as yet given back nothing he had muchhe wanted to share with the old creature 
 no more training do you require yoda assured him already know you thatwhich you need 
 then i am a jedi luke pressed no he knew he was not still lacked 
 yoda wrinkled up his wizened features not yet one thing you must confront then only then a full jedi be andconfront him you will sooner or later 
