 luke looked down at his own mechanical right hand i tried to stop him do it he would not challenge his father again he could not 
 vader humbled you when first you met him that experience waspart of your training it taught you among other things the value of patience hadyou not been so impatient to defeat vader then you could have finished your traininghere with yoda you would have been prepared 
 but i had to help my friends 
 and did you help them it was they who had to save you you achievedlittle by rushing back prematurely i fear 
 indignation melted leaving only sadness in its wake i found out darthvader was my father he whispered 
 to be a jedi luke you must confront and then go beyond the dark your father get past impatience is the easiest you like yourfather only your father was seduced by what he found on the other side of the you have held firm no longer so reckless now luke you are strongand patient and you are ready for your final confrontation 
 luke shook his head again as the implications of the old speech becameclear i do it ben 
 shoulders slumped in defeat then the emperor has alreadywon you were our only hope 
 luke reached for alternatives yoda said i could train another to 
 the other he spoke of is your twin sister the old man offered a dry will find it no easier than you to destroy darth vader 
 luke was visibly jolted by this information he stood up to face this i have a sister 
