 luke resisted this knowledge at first he neither needed nor wanted a was unique he had no missing the hand whose mechanicalreplacement he now flexed tightly pawn in a castle conspiracy cribs switched and parted and whisked away to different secret lives knew who he was he was luke skywalker born to a on a tatooine sandfarm by uncle owen and aunt beru raised in a life withoutfrills a hardworking honest his motherhis motherwhat was itabout his mother what had she said who was she what had she told him heturned his mind inward to a place and time far from the damp soil of dagobah to chamber his mother and hissister his sister 
 leia leia is my sister he exclaimed nearly falling over the stump 
 your insight serves you well ben nodded he quickly became stern your feelings deep down luke they do you credit but they could be madeto serve the emperor 
